title: Jenny Slate
description: Jenny Slate (comedy, HBO, SNL, Gabe and Jenny) is one of Pete's absolute favorite people and this conversation could've gone forever and almost did. It's one of our funniest and also deepest and weirdest eps yet. Please get into it!!! YOU WEIRDOS!!
